---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'May 13, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Spark"
  description="The rules for using Spark."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="legal">
    <article class="legal__inner">
      <p class="legal__eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="legal__title">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="legal__updated">Last updated {updated}</p>

      <p>
        By creating an account or using Spark, you agree to these Terms. If you
        don’t agree, please don’t use the app.
      </p>

      <h2>Eligibility</h2>
      <p>
        You must be at least 18 years old, legally able to enter a contract, and
        not be barred from receiving services under applicable law. We reserve
        the right to verify age and remove accounts that violate this rule.
      </p>

      <h2>Your account</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>One account per person. Don’t impersonate others or use a fake identity.</li>
        <li>You’re responsible for activity on your account. Keep your login secure.</li>
        <li>You can delete your account at any time from <strong>Settings → Account</strong>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>You agree <strong>not</strong> to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Harass, threaten, or harm other users.</li>
        <li>Post nudity, sexual content, or content involving minors.</li>
        <li>Spam, scam, or solicit money from other users.</li>
        <li>Use automated tools to scrape, copy, or interact with the app.</li>
        <li>Attempt to circumvent moderation, blocking, or safety systems.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Violations can result in immediate, permanent removal without refund.
      </p>

      <h2>User content</h2>
      <p>
        You keep ownership of the photos, text, and other content you upload.
        You grant Spark a worldwide, non-exclusive license to host, display, and
        moderate that content for the purpose of running the service. We may
        remove content at our discretion if it violates these Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Purchases &amp; coins</h2>
      <p>
        Coins and premium features are sold via Apple App Store and Google Play.
        All purchases are final and governed by the platform’s refund policy.
        Coins have no cash value, can’t be transferred between accounts, and may
        be revoked if obtained through fraud or chargeback.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimers</h2>
      <p>
        Spark is provided “as is.” We don’t guarantee a match, a date, or a
        relationship outcome. We don’t conduct background checks on users — use
        your own judgment when meeting people.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, Spark’s total liability for any
        claim is limited to the amount you paid us in the prior 12 months, or
        $50, whichever is greater.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these Terms from time to time. We’ll notify you of
        material changes in-app or by email. Continued use means you accept the
        revised Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@sparkapp.dev">hello@sparkapp.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
